{"4311030": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "給我推的Vtuber箱打賞了1億台幣之後，我得到了只屬於我的內射後宮", "steam_appid": 4311030, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆故事簡介◆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >某個VTuber事務所的全推粉主角，隨手買的彩票竟然中了10億日元！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為了推し把全額砸進打賞，數日後竟以「特別謝禮」名義被邀請到事務所！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在近未來的VR技術下，能直接觸碰推し的後宮空間中，盡情中出受孕性愛！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311030/extras/36336995f0b2278324a7fca577736640.avif?t=1771230088\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆遊戲概要◆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >類型：只要搭話就能立刻插入生中出SEX！VTuber受孕後宮RPG！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H場景：22個（全角色都有H場景）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HCG：基本22張+射精差分22張+秘密2張=合計46張</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >結局：2種</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >回想模式＆全開放功能：有</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311030/extras/2370e4cff610ccae537e506aab503928.avif?t=1771230088\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆本作特色◆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >22名H對象角色全都是主角的推しVTuber！在封閉空間內對女孩子們為所欲為的完全合法後宮體驗！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >H語音全角色個別！使用大量同人語音作品中熟悉的人氣聲優H語音數據，</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >隨著展開逐漸高漲的循環語音＆絕頂語音，實現講究的附語音H場景！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311030/extras/70f1fafb639bca1f9acfafc7d5261c5e.avif?t=1771230088\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射精倒數顯示讓射精＆絕頂時機一目了然！（可ON/OFF切換）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >射精時斷面圖顯示讓子宮中出射精的樣子清晰可見！（可ON/OFF切換）</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >HCG品質進一步進化！超色情又親切的畫風，加上多樣體位與構圖，實現連性癖都能滿足的H插圖！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >剩餘人數目標顯示與♡導引，讓遊玩無迷惘順暢進行！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311030/extras/790c0aa11387a5cb64d934fc72fa5110.avif?t=1771230088\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >畫面尺寸在ツクール製RPG中罕見的1536×1024大畫面，盡享魄力十足的H插圖！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >文字數超過7萬字！多名寫手帶來豐富多變的文本，讓大量H場景玩不膩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >附帶可快速重播H場景的回想模式！當然從遊戲開始即可全開放！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每個女主角都有攻受雙方，多樣情境與體位的本番中出場面，毎日玩也不膩！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >完全無需麻煩的等級提升或素材收集！只要對喜歡的女主角搭話就能立刻享受H場景！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311030/extras/33dee7c2171cfce00c755580a5b9cc86.avif?t=1771230088\" width=1560 height=878 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >◆H情境◆</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與慾求不滿女社長的榨精騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與天才魔術師的後背位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與廢柴神官的抱緊正常位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與男裝麗人王子樣的正常位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與笨拙機娘的站立後入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與獅子戰士的俯臥後入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與巨女幽靈的騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與不認真迷你裙警察的拘束對面座位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與緊縛抖M龍人的吊起站立後入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與冷酷忍者的騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與痴女天使的抱緊正常位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與抖S魅魔的倒立騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與不幸墮天使的抱緊正常位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與對宅男友善的辣妹黑暗精靈的對面座位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與清純系婊子狼女的騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與中二病鳳凰的後背位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與靈性女神倒立騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與賴床熊桑的種付壓</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與傲嬌獨角獸的站立後入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與超乳花魁的俯臥後入</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與病嬌蛇女的抱緊正常位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >與淫亂粉紅兔女的騎乘位</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/4311030/extras/0f98945487c6ae912f841c64a2f14b31.avif?t=1771230088\" width=1560 height=8